name: Tesco Smoked Salmon Slices 100G
description: Succulent slices of smoked salmon, smoked over beech and oak wood for a milder flavour, cured using salt and sugar, then trimmed and sliced for easy serving. Responsibly sourced from the waters around Scotland or Norway, a source of omega 3. Delicious with cream cheese in sandwiches and bagels, or in pasta dishes and quiches. For more serving suggestions go to www.tesco.com/realfood
